information: NACHTIVILLE is an indoor festival by the crew behind Nachtidigital. The festival takes place at Weissenhäuser Strand, a holiday park on the Baltic coast of Schleswig-Holstein. With NACHTIVILLE, the Nachtdigital crew wants to merge the themes of “vacation” and “rave”. Guests can choose between various apartments, bungalows and hotel rooms, in which their festival tickets are included. On 6 individual stages, including a subtropical pool party, guests will be presented with a varied program by over 60 artists from the electronic music scene.

2 STAGES | 4 DAYS | 4 NIGHTS | 50+ ARTISTS
